<Font Color=#FF0000>
<H3>BRIEF DESCRIPTION</H3>
<P>
<Font Color=#4c4c4c>
  Crossdos allows you to read and write MS-DOS (v2 or higher) formatted disks
directly from AmigaDOS. It integrates itself into the OS allowing your MS-DOS
disks to be accessed from any application.
