<Font Color=#FF0000>DISLIKES
<P>
<Font Color=#4c4c4c>
     I would have like to seen a DiskSalv type utility to fix Read/Write
     errors. MS DOS 6 has Scandisk, although Norton Utilities on the PC
     is excellent on finding a fixing common disk problems and mapping out
     bad blocks.
       The disk uses horrible standard four colour icons which are awful.
     A combination of MWB or NewIcons would have been nice for a 90s
     product.
<P>
